OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy morning with
OL,6,Foccasional rain, perhaps turning
OL,7,Fpersistent in the southeast for a
OL,8,Ftime. Brightening up in the afternoon
OL,9,Fwith heavy showers and a chance of
OL,10,Fthunder.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FShowers or longer spells of
OL,13,Frain spread in through the evening and
OL,14,Fovernight, the rain heavy at times.
OL,15,FWindy around the coasts.
OL,16,
OL,17,CThursday:FBright or sunny spells and
OL,18,Fscattered showers. Becoming dry for a
OL,19,Ftime in the evening as showers fade
OL,20,Fout before cloud and rain arrive
OL,21,Fovernight. Breezy around the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
