OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FCloud
OL,6,Fand rain clear east Friday morning,
OL,7,Fwith bright spells and showers
OL,8,Ffollowing. Bright spells and showers
OL,9,Fon Saturday. Dry and bright on Sunday.
